It is hard enough to navigate the markets Dave. Politics on Twitter invariably morphs into vitriol and brings out the unattractive and combative side of people. Moreover, I am not going to change anyone's political views and vice versa.

I have purposefully eliminated most if not all of my political comments over the last year - and I will continue to do so. I concluded that it was counter productive to respectful and constructive debate on Twitter.
